\/African_National_Congress\" title=\"African National Congress\">African National Congress<\/a> during the days when the organization was banned. She was also active in <a href=\"http:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/HIV\/AIDS\" title=\"HIV\/AIDS\">HIV\/AIDS<\/a> causes.<\/p>","name":"Nadine Gordimer","place_of_birth":"Springs, Gauteng ,  Johannesburg ,  South Africa","place_of_death":"Johannesburg, South Africa","text":"Nadine Gordimer , Literature, 1991","year":1991.0}